{"title":"朝中友谊之歌","authors":["德烈译"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":10,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝中友谊之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朝鲜民歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在牡丹峰山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起重机挥动着；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天安门上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平鸽自由飞翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们放声歌唱春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱，新亚洲明媚的春天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们放声歌唱和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱朝中人民紧握双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用斗争赢得的和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二平壤的千里马歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响彻云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像东方的朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒四射。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱朝中人民牢不可破的友谊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们站在光荣的一条战线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了共同的目的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远纵情高歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三长白山的松柏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肃然耸立在山尖上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上甘岭战壕的吹号声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，还像在我们耳边震响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军指战员的英雄业绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像永恒不灭的珍奇传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万古流传！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔德烈译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}